description: The End of the Earth devastates in part 6 of this earth blistering epic! Plus: Doctor Octopus has a new Sinister Six-THE AVENGERS! Can Spider-Man sacrifice one life to save the entire planet?
name: Ends of the Earth, Part 6: Everyone Dies

description: Scourge's secret identity revealed! What are this new vigilante's motivations, and what connection does Scourge have to Diamondback?
name: Shock to the System, Part 3

description: Deadpool has been beaten badly. Who could have managed to best the Merc with a Mouth? The dumbest member of...the Intelligencia?! Guest-starring Taskmaster!
name: Deadpool Reborn, Part 2: Master of My Own Domain

description:
CORY WALKER RETURNS TO INVINCIBLE… AGAIN!

What has been going on with Monster Girl and Robot? What happened to them while they were in the Flaxan dimension? All answers will be revealed – starting now!

Meanwhile, trouble is brewing in the present and the New Invincible is already in over his head! All this – and where is Mark Grayson?!

The Fantastic Four travel to the country of Wakanda, which means the return of Black Panther to the pages of Fantastic Four. Their mission is: what happens when the world completely runs out of Vibranium?
name: Inert

description: Includes a free Buster mini-comic pullout in the centre pages, featuring both reprinted strips and new ones commissioned especially for the promotion.

name: To zap or not to zap ?
Tu verras quand tu seras grand
Nous venons chaque année sur la tome de nos parents...
Le retour de Billy the Cat

description: Brian Pulido delivers the last chapter of Lady Death’s tragic origin in this action packed finale to the Cursed arc. And though she will survive…her life will never be the same again. Available with a sexy Regular painted cover by Jason Eden, a Wraparound by Michael Dipascale and a Sultry cover by Richard Ortiz. Also available with a special Art Deco Retailer Order Incentive by painter Dipascale!

Vampirella -- still reeling from the horrible fate of her ally, Sofia, and the rebirth of her old enemy, Von Kriest -- charges back into battle as more old foes resurface, some offering a truce. But is the enemy of her enemy really a friend?
